td.p:
the goods pawned shall upon the expiration of
                                4 lunar months from the date of advancing the money on loan become,
                                if they are not earlier redeemed, the property of the pawnbroker;

if before the expiration of 4 lunar months
                                from the date of advancing the money on loan, you wish to continue
                                the loan you may do so subject to your paying the interest then due;
